1
00:01:17,811 --> 00:01:19,176
I'm late

2
00:01:25,018 --> 00:01:27,077
It's nice of you to rush back

3
00:01:28,488 --> 00:01:29,682
Where is everybody?

4
00:01:29,856 --> 00:01:32,290
They've all gone to the funeral

5
00:01:33,193 --> 00:01:34,683
Take along an umbrella

6
00:02:45,431 --> 00:02:49,697
Teacher!

7
00:02:52,272 --> 00:02:55,207
Chen!

8
00:02:57,377 --> 00:02:59,971
Teacher's beyond hearing

9
00:03:01,814 --> 00:03:04,180
Chen!

10
00:03:10,423 --> 00:03:13,017
What's the matter with you?

11
00:03:18,831 --> 00:03:21,493
Take him back for a rest

12
00:05:17,984 --> 00:05:19,611
Have some porridge!

13
00:05:23,189 --> 00:05:25,054
You haven't eaten in two days

14
00:05:26,259 --> 00:05:30,696
Teacher's dead
I know how you feel

15
00:05:31,597 --> 00:05:33,963
But it hurts me

16
00:05:34,133 --> 00:05:37,159
to see you like this

17
00:05:42,475 --> 00:05:45,467
Please, eat something

18
00:06:18,411 --> 00:06:20,242
He still refused to eat?

19
00:06:20,913 --> 00:06:23,211
Talk to him

20
00:06:28,621 --> 00:06:32,113
Why won't you eat?

21
00:06:32,291 --> 00:06:35,021
We all feel sad ever his death

22
00:06:35,194 --> 00:06:38,823
But we must live on

23
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,428
Can ulcers kill a man?

24
00:06:44,470 --> 00:06:48,338
He had ulcers but died of pneumonia

25
00:06:49,308 --> 00:06:52,175
Can that kill a man?

26
00:06:58,518 --> 00:07:02,921
How did he die?

27
00:07:04,257 --> 00:07:05,884
The doctor said

28
00:07:06,058 --> 00:07:08,288
he died of pneumonia

29
00:07:08,461 --> 00:07:09,894
I don't believe it

30
00:07:11,431 --> 00:07:16,198
He was in perfect health
How did he die?

31
00:07:16,369 --> 00:07:17,859
Something must have happened

32
00:07:18,037 --> 00:07:24,442
Calm yourself

33
00:07:24,911 --> 00:07:27,675
We've all been thinking about it

34
00:07:28,314 --> 00:07:29,804
But we mustn't be rash

35
00:07:29,982 --> 00:07:33,281
We are investigation quietly

36
00:07:33,453 --> 00:07:34,818
I must find out the truth

37
00:07:34,987 --> 00:07:36,249
of course

38
00:07:36,422 --> 00:07:39,914
It's our duty too

39
00:07:40,092 --> 00:07:41,787
Many people will come

40
00:07:41,961 --> 00:07:43,360
to pay homage tomorrow

41
00:07:43,529 --> 00:07:47,863
You must be calm
Get some rest

42
00:07:48,634 --> 00:07:51,967
Ho Yuan-chia was a great instructor

43
00:07:52,138 --> 00:07:54,936
He was a champion of the weak

44
00:07:55,107 --> 00:07:58,599
Everyone knows that

45
00:07:58,778 --> 00:08:02,509
I've known him for 30 years

46
00:08:02,682 --> 00:08:05,048
I admire him

47
00:08:05,218 --> 00:08:09,985
for founding Ching Wu School

48
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:16,760
He traveling all over the country

49
00:08:17,263 --> 00:08:23,202
Using up all his money and energy

50
00:08:23,369 --> 00:08:25,803
He even sacrificed his life

51
00:08:25,972 --> 00:08:29,032
I remember what he used to say

52
00:08:29,208 --> 00:08:33,645
His purpose in founding Ching Wu School

53
00:08:33,813 --> 00:08:38,944
was to strengthen the mind and body

54
00:08:39,118 --> 00:08:41,951
not to aim at winning over others

55
00:08:42,121 --> 00:08:45,488
He was against conflict among schools

56
00:08:45,658 --> 00:08:51,619
He hoped all of us
would be of one heart

57
00:08:51,864 --> 00:08:54,424
to be strong and love the country

58
00:08:55,401 --> 00:08:57,369
We must remember

59
00:08:57,537 --> 00:09:01,405
his words

60
00:09:01,707 --> 00:09:07,509
and develop martial arts accordingly

61
00:09:07,813 --> 00:09:09,906
that every Chinese

62
00:09:10,349 --> 00:09:12,613
will be strong

63
00:09:12,785 --> 00:09:17,119
to serve the community and the country

64
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:22,289
as well as the future generation

65
00:09:23,829 --> 00:09:27,128
He died soon

66
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:31,361
after Ching Wu School began

67
00:09:31,837 --> 00:09:35,329
He contributed so much

68
00:09:35,775 --> 00:09:39,438
to martial arts

69
00:09:39,612 --> 00:09:42,445
We have lost a great man

70
00:09:42,915 --> 00:09:45,543
our respects to Master Ho!

71
00:09:45,718 --> 00:09:48,915
Let us have 3 minutes' silence

72
00:09:55,761 --> 00:09:56,989
Please sign your name

73
00:09:57,363 --> 00:10:00,025
We're just in time

74
00:10:00,499 --> 00:10:02,091
You're...?

75
00:10:02,468 --> 00:10:04,766
I'm interpreter for Hungkiu School's

76
00:10:04,937 --> 00:10:06,928
Mr. Hu

77
00:10:07,106 --> 00:10:10,473
I've brought something for you

78
00:10:23,756 --> 00:10:25,587
What is it?

79
00:10:26,125 --> 00:10:30,061
Chief Ling Mu Kuan sent me

80
00:10:40,006 --> 00:10:41,337
Sick Man of East Asia?

81
00:10:43,709 --> 00:10:44,937
What do you mean by that?

82
00:10:45,111 --> 00:10:48,512
It's very simple

83
00:10:48,681 --> 00:10:51,343
We know you're training here

84
00:10:51,517 --> 00:10:54,782
The name is a gift from our master

85
00:10:57,623 --> 00:11:00,524
Are you a Chinese?

86
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:07,456
Yes, but I'm different from you

87
00:11:09,201 --> 00:11:13,934
Calm down
I won't come if I'm afraid

88
00:11:14,106 --> 00:11:16,131
I know you are all here

89
00:11:16,475 --> 00:11:19,069
I come to challenge you

90
00:11:19,945 --> 00:11:23,506
Well? Who'll step out?

91
00:11:25,217 --> 00:11:26,741
Chia Chi

92
00:11:43,469 --> 00:11:44,993
Step back!

93
00:11:45,171 --> 00:11:47,469
My friends here are eager for a dual

94
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:50,370
Who will satisfy them?

95
00:11:57,183 --> 00:12:00,243
You have trained hard

96
00:12:00,419 --> 00:12:04,185
but now you dare not speak out

97
00:12:10,196 --> 00:12:13,427
What's happened to your courage?

98
00:12:26,712 --> 00:12:31,706
Hold it. You're...?

99
00:12:31,884 --> 00:12:35,581
I'm Hu, the interpreter

100
00:12:36,889 --> 00:12:39,915
our teacher told us

101
00:12:40,459 --> 00:12:42,689
to train for physical fitness

102
00:12:42,862 --> 00:12:44,489
but not for fights

103
00:12:44,864 --> 00:12:48,459
our school won't fight you

104
00:12:50,269 --> 00:12:53,466
Then you're conceding defeat

105
00:12:57,309 --> 00:12:58,537
If anyone can defeat me,

106
00:12:58,711 --> 00:13:01,339
I'll eat those words

107
00:13:02,281 --> 00:13:05,580
Listen to my Japanese friends

108
00:13:05,751 --> 00:13:10,586
They've made a bet

109
00:13:11,090 --> 00:13:13,820
Well? Anyone care to try?

110
00:13:14,727 --> 00:13:16,524
If the Ching Wu people won't fight

111
00:13:16,695 --> 00:13:19,926
how about the other schools?

112
00:13:20,099 --> 00:13:24,900
Well? You want to; K

113
00:13:25,671 --> 00:13:28,572
Don't be mad, kid

114
00:13:28,741 --> 00:13:33,235
You're all useless sick man of Asia

115
00:13:33,412 --> 00:13:39,908
Chen, hold yourself

116
00:13:43,255 --> 00:13:48,887
Why won't you speak up?

117
00:13:51,397 --> 00:13:54,855
You can all attack together

118
00:13:55,034 --> 00:13:58,231
We shall always oblige

119
00:14:10,316 --> 00:14:14,343
It's too much, too much!

120
00:14:15,554 --> 00:14:18,387
Why won't you let us fight?

121
00:14:19,091 --> 00:14:21,685
I wanted to fight too

122
00:14:22,661 --> 00:14:26,791
But teacher told us not to get in trouble

123
00:15:09,675 --> 00:15:11,233
Whom do you want?

124
00:15:14,513 --> 00:15:17,505
Your chief, Hiroshi Suzuki

125
00:15:20,352 --> 00:15:24,049
He's not here
What is it?

126
00:15:25,624 --> 00:15:27,615
I have something to return to him

127
00:15:48,514 --> 00:15:52,109
You really get the nerve

128
00:15:53,085 --> 00:15:56,612
I'm the worst of Ching Wu students

129
00:16:01,827 --> 00:16:06,491
I want to try your Japanese martial arts

130
00:16:20,946 --> 00:16:23,107
You must be tried of living!

131
00:16:23,615 --> 00:16:25,640
Let's me teach you something

132
00:16:25,818 --> 00:16:32,280
Will fight alone or in group?

133
00:16:32,458 --> 00:16:34,517
Just myself is enough

134
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,537
I have it

135
00:17:21,073 --> 00:17:21,903
Surround him

136
00:20:08,941 --> 00:20:09,839
Hold it!

137
00:22:23,075 --> 00:22:30,208
We Chinese aren't sick man

138
00:23:19,798 --> 00:23:21,789
Eat

139
00:23:26,004 --> 00:23:28,438
You eat paper this time

140
00:23:29,207 --> 00:23:32,005
Next time will be glasses

141
00:23:55,267 --> 00:24:01,399
What is it! Are you mad!

142
00:24:06,945 --> 00:24:08,640
Here we are. Pull over

143
00:24:31,736 --> 00:24:37,174
Ching Wu people dared come to our gate!

144
00:24:47,986 --> 00:24:49,248
What's his name?

145
00:24:52,491 --> 00:24:55,085
I know him, Master

146
00:24:55,260 --> 00:24:58,058
He's Chen, Ho's favorite

147
00:25:00,632 --> 00:25:02,031
Let me ask you this

148
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,565
Could we <i>Bushido</i> people

149
00:25:03,735 --> 00:25:05,635
take it lying down?

150
00:25:06,972 --> 00:25:07,996
As a master of Japanese martial arts

151
00:25:08,173 --> 00:25:09,162
we won't be bullied easily

152
00:25:09,341 --> 00:25:10,239
Right

153
00:25:10,342 --> 00:25:13,971
Bushido is the world's best

154
00:25:14,913 --> 00:25:18,815
Now tell me what to do

155
00:25:19,017 --> 00:25:20,006
We must take revenge!

156
00:25:20,185 --> 00:25:24,588
Right, revenge!

157
00:25:24,956 --> 00:25:31,828
Smash up the Ching Wu School

158
00:25:32,097 --> 00:25:35,225
Don't come back if you fail

159
00:26:09,134 --> 00:26:10,658
What is it?

160
00:26:10,835 --> 00:26:11,426
Go in and take a look

161
00:26:11,603 --> 00:26:12,968
No

162
00:26:26,251 --> 00:26:27,912
Where's the dog?

163
00:26:29,387 --> 00:26:32,379
It belongs to a foreigner

164
00:26:39,864 --> 00:26:41,695
Come here!

165
00:26:48,607 --> 00:26:52,509
Don't you want to get in?

166
00:26:52,777 --> 00:26:55,371
Come on

167
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:59,741
Act like a dog and I'll get you in

168
00:27:34,052 --> 00:27:36,987
Hurry, the police are coming!

169
00:28:26,337 --> 00:28:27,395
What do you want?

170
00:29:06,377 --> 00:29:08,242
You attacked without warning

171
00:29:16,454 --> 00:29:17,478
What's the purpose?

172
00:29:19,224 --> 00:29:20,248
Why all this rough stuff?

173
00:29:26,264 --> 00:29:27,492
Take that down

174
00:30:42,473 --> 00:30:44,100
Don't fight, stop fighting

175
00:31:03,228 --> 00:31:04,718
Don't insult our teacher

176
00:31:24,148 --> 00:31:25,638
Stop!

177
00:31:26,251 --> 00:31:32,383
Right, let's go!

178
00:31:35,026 --> 00:31:39,622
That's only a little warning

179
00:31:39,797 --> 00:31:42,357
Hand over Chen three days

180
00:31:42,667 --> 00:31:45,568
or we'll have you closed down

181
00:31:45,870 --> 00:31:48,771
and you'll all be arrested

182
00:32:04,088 --> 00:32:06,181
Brother!

183
00:32:06,491 --> 00:32:07,719
Come and help

184
00:32:18,503 --> 00:32:22,803
Teacher, if you had been alive

185
00:32:23,942 --> 00:32:26,877
We wouldn't have been bullied like this

186
00:32:37,088 --> 00:32:39,283
He wants us to hand over Chen

187
00:32:39,457 --> 00:32:42,483
His rashness got us into trouble

188
00:32:42,660 --> 00:32:44,719
Don't blame him

189
00:32:44,896 --> 00:32:47,091
Don't blame it on him

190
00:32:47,598 --> 00:32:49,361
He's back

191
00:32:56,007 --> 00:32:56,837
Salute

192
00:32:57,008 --> 00:33:01,308
You got us into trouble

193
00:33:01,679 --> 00:33:05,115
Where have you been all day?

194
00:33:05,283 --> 00:33:07,979
Did you go to Hungkiu School?

195
00:33:10,855 --> 00:33:13,050
You want to be a hero

196
00:33:13,224 --> 00:33:15,192
Look what happened to us

197
00:33:15,360 --> 00:33:17,385
Why didn't you tell us?

198
00:33:23,601 --> 00:33:24,761
Listen

199
00:33:24,936 --> 00:33:26,597
We build our body

200
00:33:26,771 --> 00:33:28,671
and love our country?

201
00:33:30,875 --> 00:33:32,968
But not fight and make trouble

202
00:33:34,545 --> 00:33:37,309
Then why didn't you tell us?

203
00:33:37,482 --> 00:33:38,574
Many Japanese came

204
00:33:38,750 --> 00:33:40,081
and beat us up

205
00:33:40,251 --> 00:33:41,980
They asked us to hand
you over in three days

206
00:33:42,153 --> 00:33:43,484
What shall we do?

207
00:33:44,422 --> 00:33:46,390
Let him finish what he started

208
00:33:46,557 --> 00:33:48,354
How can you say that?

209
00:33:48,526 --> 00:33:49,493
What then?

210
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:51,059
Wait to be closed down?

211
00:33:51,229 --> 00:33:51,991
Not only that

212
00:33:52,163 --> 00:33:53,790
We'll all be arrested

213
00:33:54,932 --> 00:33:56,456
Think!

214
00:33:56,634 --> 00:33:57,965
We must not deliver him to them

215
00:33:58,136 --> 00:34:00,331
and we must protect all of us too

216
00:34:03,274 --> 00:34:05,333
We can't surrender him

217
00:34:05,877 --> 00:34:08,243
or he'll be killed for sure

218
00:34:08,579 --> 00:34:11,980
There's only one way
Leave Shanghai

219
00:34:13,284 --> 00:34:15,752
Right
You must leave Shanghai

220
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:17,080
Not me

221
00:34:17,255 --> 00:34:18,381
Why not?

222
00:34:18,556 --> 00:34:20,023
I don't want to get
you into trouble

223
00:34:22,193 --> 00:34:23,956
We all understand

224
00:34:24,128 --> 00:34:28,155
You must think for yourself too

225
00:34:29,133 --> 00:34:30,157
I'm not leaving

226
00:34:30,334 --> 00:34:32,859
You'd better leave

227
00:34:33,037 --> 00:34:33,969
If they can't find you

228
00:34:34,138 --> 00:34:37,005
despite Japanese influence

229
00:34:37,175 --> 00:34:40,338
They can't do anything without proof

230
00:34:40,945 --> 00:34:42,936
I didn't mean
what I just said

231
00:34:43,114 --> 00:34:44,240
We're brothers

232
00:34:44,415 --> 00:34:46,713
I can't let you die

233
00:35:08,506 --> 00:35:10,872
You don't want to leave now

234
00:35:11,042 --> 00:35:13,033
Do you think staying is a brave thing?

235
00:35:14,445 --> 00:35:16,072
None of us is afraid to trouble

236
00:35:16,247 --> 00:35:17,805
Why don't you listen to our advise?

237
00:35:22,787 --> 00:35:24,220
Go

238
00:35:24,388 --> 00:35:25,855
We won't blame you

239
00:35:26,724 --> 00:35:27,588
Go, go

240
00:35:27,758 --> 00:35:29,350
We won't blame you

241
00:35:33,097 --> 00:35:36,328
Have you forgotten

242
00:35:36,501 --> 00:35:38,162
What teacher always said?

243
00:35:40,238 --> 00:35:43,036
You know the principle of our school

244
00:35:43,207 --> 00:35:46,540
His death increases our burden

245
00:35:46,711 --> 00:35:49,942
Think of the school if not yourself

246
00:35:50,281 --> 00:35:52,511
Why sacrifice needlessly

247
00:35:53,251 --> 00:35:54,081
As you elder

248
00:35:54,252 --> 00:35:56,447
I order you to go

249
00:35:59,023 --> 00:36:02,424
Buy him a train ticket for tomorrow

250
00:36:51,509 --> 00:36:53,238
It's late, you'd better sleep

251
00:36:55,012 --> 00:36:56,070
Is everything packed?

252
00:36:56,247 --> 00:36:57,646
Yes

253
00:37:03,354 --> 00:37:07,051
I came back to marry you

254
00:37:10,127 --> 00:37:12,186
but look what's happened

255
00:37:13,030 --> 00:37:15,021
I don't care much for ceremony

256
00:37:15,199 --> 00:37:18,635
We can return to Shanghai some other day

257
00:37:18,803 --> 00:37:20,532
We can have great fun then

258
00:37:23,107 --> 00:37:25,769
Friends suffer because of me

259
00:37:26,344 --> 00:37:29,541
Nobody is blaming you

260
00:37:29,714 --> 00:37:33,445
It's the first train
Go to sleep

261
00:37:33,985 --> 00:37:40,356
I must stay with Teacher tonight

262
00:38:01,012 --> 00:38:03,105
You go to sleep first

263
00:39:36,140 --> 00:39:37,437
Did anyone see you?

264
00:39:38,409 --> 00:39:40,104
No. They're all asleep

265
00:39:41,212 --> 00:39:41,974
Got it?

266
00:39:42,346 --> 00:39:44,871
Yes. Mr. Wu told us to get away

267
00:39:45,249 --> 00:39:47,615
If they found out Ho died of this

268
00:39:47,785 --> 00:39:49,616
We'd be in deep trouble

269
00:39:50,121 --> 00:39:52,521
Why does Mr. Wu want us to leave?

270
00:39:53,357 --> 00:39:56,155
He said the job's done

271
00:39:56,327 --> 00:39:58,386
There's no point tarrying

272
00:39:59,830 --> 00:40:02,924
What should we do?

273
00:40:04,135 --> 00:40:05,796
You're returning home tomorrow

274
00:40:05,970 --> 00:40:06,994
I'll resign

275
00:40:07,171 --> 00:40:09,833
And we'll go together

276
00:40:17,915 --> 00:40:19,007
You're Japanese?

277
00:40:19,383 --> 00:40:20,145
Yes

278
00:40:20,751 --> 00:40:24,380
I came to kill Ho Yuan-chia

279
00:40:24,555 --> 00:40:26,455
How could you
say such words?

280
00:40:26,624 --> 00:40:29,457
Why not?
I'm not afraid of your Fist of Fury

281
00:40:30,428 --> 00:40:33,158
You're Ho's favorite pupil

282
00:40:33,864 --> 00:40:35,456
I must test your mettle

283
00:41:22,346 --> 00:41:37,319
Feng, come out here

284
00:42:12,863 --> 00:42:14,660
Why did you kill Teacher?

285
00:42:15,866 --> 00:42:17,857
Why did you kill Teacher?

286
00:42:21,038 --> 00:42:23,131
Why did you kill Teacher?

287
00:43:02,546 --> 00:43:03,706
Teacher was killed by
poison in the biscuit

288
00:43:03,881 --> 00:43:06,941
I'll all find out the murderer
and make revenge

289
00:43:16,026 --> 00:43:18,017
Captain! Captain!

290
00:43:25,536 --> 00:43:28,232
Big Brother

291
00:43:30,808 --> 00:43:31,775
Where is Big Brother?

292
00:43:32,142 --> 00:43:33,541
What's it?

293
00:43:33,777 --> 00:43:36,302
