01:11:21,777 --> 01:11:25,838
Yes, Japanese is
influential in Shanghai

583
01:11:26,949 --> 01:11:29,645
They very well may close down the School

584
01:11:30,552 --> 01:11:33,680
What if they found Chen?

585
01:11:33,856 --> 01:11:35,289
He'll surely be killed

586
01:11:35,457 --> 01:11:37,118
How can we let them found him out?

587
01:11:38,193 --> 01:11:40,058
I wonder where
he's hiding

588
01:11:40,229 --> 01:11:43,221
We must find him
and tell him to escape

589
01:11:43,599 --> 01:11:44,566
I...

590
01:11:49,038 --> 01:11:50,005
You what?

591
01:12:04,887 --> 01:12:06,684
You know where he is?

592
01:12:16,198 --> 01:12:18,393
It is a matter of life or death

593
01:12:18,701 --> 01:12:21,670
If you know,
don't be silent

594
01:12:29,078 --> 01:12:30,909
I know where he is at night

595
01:12:31,347 --> 01:12:33,440
Where is he now?

596
01:13:15,224 --> 01:13:17,988
I'm from the
telephone company

597
01:13:18,293 --> 01:13:21,558
What took you so long?

598
01:13:22,097 --> 01:13:24,190
I just got my orders

599
01:13:24,733 --> 01:13:27,725
Come with me!

600
01:13:34,009 --> 01:13:34,998
There

601
01:16:27,015 --> 01:16:29,381
Don't just stand there,
hurry up!

602
01:16:44,433 --> 01:16:47,493
There's another one inside

603
01:17:06,321 --> 01:17:07,652
Wait here

604
01:17:19,267 --> 01:17:21,633
The telephone man is here

605
01:17:23,605 --> 01:17:25,163
Master, it's the telephone man

606
01:17:25,340 --> 01:17:26,534
Come in!

607
01:17:27,109 --> 01:17:28,007
Tell him to come in

608
01:17:28,510 --> 01:17:30,034
Come here

609
01:17:42,958 --> 01:17:45,017
Chief, it's the telephone man

610
01:17:45,494 --> 01:17:46,324
Go on

611
01:17:58,206 --> 01:17:59,798
I am dying to find Chen

612
01:18:00,108 --> 01:18:03,168
and see just how good he is

613
01:18:03,545 --> 01:18:06,241
It's not only his Fist of Fury

614
01:18:06,548 --> 01:18:08,880
He moves like lightning

615
01:18:09,418 --> 01:18:11,648
I think we need not to fight

616
01:18:11,820 --> 01:18:14,152
We'll concentrate
on Ching Wu School

617
01:18:14,956 --> 01:18:16,753
Wait!

618
01:18:28,837 --> 01:18:29,633
Okay

619
01:18:49,257 --> 01:18:50,349
What do you suggest?

620
01:18:50,826 --> 01:18:53,954
Kill all of them in one stroke

621
01:18:54,730 --> 01:18:56,357
How about the consequences?

622
01:18:56,665 --> 01:18:59,099
We're the International Settlement

623
01:18:59,267 --> 01:19:00,632
As long as we
leave no evidence

624
01:19:00,802 --> 01:19:03,930
Nobody can prove a thing

625
01:19:06,041 --> 01:19:08,601
Send someone tonight

626
01:19:08,777 --> 01:19:09,835
Do a clean job

627
01:19:10,011 --> 01:19:10,909
Yes, sir!

628
01:19:21,656 --> 01:19:22,623
Why isn't he here?

629
01:19:24,192 --> 01:19:25,489
Look around

630
01:19:27,629 --> 01:19:39,029
Chen!

631
01:19:40,242 --> 01:19:41,470
I wonder where
he could have gone?

632
01:19:44,246 --> 01:19:45,679
Let's wait for him

633
01:19:48,183 --> 01:19:49,241
Where could he be?

634
01:19:50,385 --> 01:19:51,977
I wonder

635
01:20:09,671 --> 01:20:12,538
Won ton noodle

636
01:21:02,257 --> 01:21:08,218
I'm here to avenge my teacher

637
01:21:09,231 --> 01:21:24,511
It's none of your business
Get out!

638
01:21:27,816 --> 01:21:28,840
Scram!

639
01:21:37,559 --> 01:21:38,753
Scram!

640
01:24:12,814 --> 01:24:16,113
Hold it!
Who are you?

641
01:24:17,252 --> 01:24:21,279
I'm Chen
I want your master

642
01:24:21,456 --> 01:24:22,582
Chen?

643
01:25:07,836 --> 01:25:09,667
Let me take care of him.

644
01:32:04,986 --> 01:32:08,046
Li-erh!

645
01:32:08,222 --> 01:32:14,024
Yao Chang!

646
01:32:15,663 --> 01:32:17,392
What happened?
Who did it?

647
01:32:17,932 --> 01:32:21,095
Japanese

648
01:32:21,869 --> 01:32:22,961
What bout the others?

649
01:32:23,137 --> 01:32:24,104
Any survivors?

650
01:32:25,439 --> 01:32:27,839
Everyone...

651
01:32:30,411 --> 01:32:33,608
Yao Chang!

652
01:32:58,506 --> 01:33:01,942
He might yet pull through

653
01:33:04,378 --> 01:33:05,970
Help those who have a chance

654
01:33:06,147 --> 01:33:07,205
We'll go upstairs and see

655
01:33:18,259 --> 01:33:19,749
If there are any survivors

656
01:33:37,612 --> 01:33:41,070
None, Captain

657
01:34:13,381 --> 01:34:16,214
I'm unworthy of Teacher!

658
01:34:17,385 --> 01:34:19,444
I'm unworthy of Teacher!

659
01:34:22,990 --> 01:34:26,619
They died so horribly

660
01:34:27,061 --> 01:34:29,393
What are we going to do?

661
01:34:31,999 --> 01:34:35,059
Our inaction was a mistake

662
01:34:36,337 --> 01:34:38,237
Chen was right

663
01:34:40,808 --> 01:34:41,900
Japanese

664
01:34:43,044 --> 01:34:46,104
I'm from the consulate

665
01:34:46,380 --> 01:34:48,211
You dared kill
at the judo hall

666
01:34:48,382 --> 01:34:49,212
It's really too much!

667
01:34:49,383 --> 01:34:50,907
I don't want this
to get out of hands

668
01:34:51,085 --> 01:34:53,781
I'll hand over
the man to you

669
01:34:54,088 --> 01:34:56,454
You're Chinese
I don't trust you

670
01:34:56,757 --> 01:34:57,849
I must go in

671
01:35:00,061 --> 01:35:03,519
All right, just you

672
01:35:04,932 --> 01:35:07,628
Keep guard here
Admit no one

673
01:35:30,791 --> 01:35:31,951
What's up?

674
01:35:33,160 --> 01:35:35,754
The Japanese did it

675
01:35:36,497 --> 01:35:37,225
The Japanese?

676
01:35:37,398 --> 01:35:38,422
Watch your tongue

677
01:35:38,599 --> 01:35:41,864
You must not slander people

678
01:35:42,336 --> 01:35:43,303
What proof do you have?

679
01:35:44,972 --> 01:35:46,599
These two survivors

680
01:35:47,007 --> 01:35:48,872
If I wasrt in charge
of Ching Wu School

681
01:35:49,043 --> 01:35:51,568
If not for Ching Wu
School's future

682
01:35:51,746 --> 01:35:53,577
I'd fight you to the end

683
01:35:54,281 --> 01:35:55,805
Stop talking

684
01:35:55,983 --> 01:35:57,917
Go ahead and
file a complaint

685
01:35:58,085 --> 01:35:59,313
I don't care anything

686
01:35:59,487 --> 01:36:01,717
I only want
Chen immediately

687
01:36:06,227 --> 01:36:09,094
He killed many people
in Hungkiu School

688
01:36:09,830 --> 01:36:12,094
The consulate has
asked the police for him

689
01:36:12,433 --> 01:36:14,663
You'll have to
hand over Chen

690
01:36:14,835 --> 01:36:15,529
What?

691
01:36:15,703 --> 01:36:17,432
They killed so many
of us but are free

692
01:36:17,605 --> 01:36:20,768
And nobody knows if Chen

693
01:36:20,941 --> 01:36:22,101
Was the killer
at Hungkiu School

694
01:36:22,276 --> 01:36:23,709
Now you want us
to hand him over

695
01:36:23,878 --> 01:36:26,608
Is that fair?

696
01:36:32,219 --> 01:36:34,380
We Chinese are not
in good standing

697
01:36:39,093 --> 01:36:43,427
You know the situation here

698
01:36:43,597 --> 01:36:46,760
Chen must be delivered!

699
01:36:47,334 --> 01:36:48,528
I don't know where he is

700
01:36:48,702 --> 01:36:50,329
Now, you call the play

701
01:36:51,372 --> 01:36:53,738
Right
Take them away!

702
01:36:58,245 --> 01:37:00,236
You really don't know
where he is?

703
01:37:39,720 --> 01:37:43,952
What if we can't find Chen?

704
01:37:44,425 --> 01:37:46,859
I've been kind to you

705
01:37:47,394 --> 01:37:50,056
Now I cannot help
you any longer

706
01:37:50,231 --> 01:37:51,664
You're taking us all in?

707
01:37:52,366 --> 01:37:55,233
Not only you'll go to prison

708
01:37:55,536 --> 01:37:57,367
but your school will be closed too

709
01:37:57,538 --> 01:37:59,836
Ching Wu School is finished

710
01:38:00,007 --> 01:38:01,770
Do you Japanese
listen to justice?

711
01:38:01,942 --> 01:38:03,534
Isn't there a law?

712
01:38:03,711 --> 01:38:05,872
I'm the law in Shanghai

713
01:38:06,046 --> 01:38:07,536
Don't blame me

714
01:38:08,082 --> 01:38:10,243
Blame it on Chen

715
01:38:10,851 --> 01:38:13,217
Who asked him to
go into hiding?

716
01:38:15,356 --> 01:38:18,223
He should surrender
for your sake

717
01:38:22,062 --> 01:38:23,654
Chen is here!

718
01:39:31,999 --> 01:39:33,557
Now tell the truth

719
01:39:34,535 --> 01:39:35,934
No lies

720
01:39:37,204 --> 01:39:39,069
If I surrender

721
01:39:40,474 --> 01:39:43,307
will you spare
Ching Wu School?

722
01:39:48,248 --> 01:39:49,180
Well?

723
01:39:54,555 --> 01:39:55,749
I can give you
my word of honor

724
01:39:56,223 --> 01:39:59,192
Don't forget,
I'm also a Chinese

725
01:40:15,509 --> 01:40:20,708
I shall pay for the lives I took

726
01:40:21,782 --> 01:40:23,841
Leave Ching Wu School alone

727
01:40:30,224 --> 01:40:35,821
Who says knight errantry is dead?

728
01:40:36,463 --> 01:40:43,198
Who says life is always preferred?

729
01:40:59,853 --> 01:41:05,155
Here goes a true hero

730
01:41:05,526 --> 01:41:14,025
Caring little what lies ahead

